descriptionNullable:
This data set was created by using weather data service and ibb open data portal .Here, there is a data set containing the time-dependent dam occupancy rate and 2 data sets showing the change of weather conditions over time. While examining the data set, you can examine the effect of weather events on the abundance rate.



Description of dataset columns =>

DATE : Date of the data collection
GENERAL_DAM_OCCUPANCY_RATE: General occupancy rate of the dam (in percentage)
GENERAL_DAM_RESERVED_WATER: Reserved water amount in the dam (in cubic meters)
name: Name of the weather station
tempmax: Maximum temperature of the day (in Celsius)
tempmin: Minimum temperature of the day (in Celsius)
temp: Average temperature of the day (in Celsius)
feelslikemax: Maximum "feels like" temperature of the day (in Celsius)
feelslikemin: Minimum "feels like" temperature of the day (in Celsius)
feelslike: Average "feels like" temperature of the day (in Celsius)
dew: Dew point temperature of the day (in Celsius)
humidity: Relative humidity of the day (in percentage)
precip: Total precipitation of the day (in millimeters)
precipprob: Probability of precipitation (in percentage)
precipcover: Precipitation cover (in percentage)
preciptype: Type of precipitation (e.g. rain, snow, etc.)
snow: Total snowfall of the day (in centimeters)
snowdepth: Snow depth (in centimeters)
windgust: Maximum wind gust speed of the day (in kilometers per hour)
windspeed: Average wind speed of the day (in kilometers per hour)
winddir: Wind direction of the day (in degrees)
sealevelpressure: Mean sea level pressure of the day (in hectopascals)
cloudcover: Cloud cover (in percentage)
visibility: Visibility (in kilometers)
solarradiation: Solar radiation (in watts per square meter)
solarenergy: Total solar energy of the day (in megajoules per square meter)
uvindex: UV index of the day
severerisk: Severity risk of the day (currently not available)
sunrise: Sunrise time of the day
sunset: Sunset time of the day
moonphase: Moon phase of the day (in degrees)
conditions: Weather conditions (e.g. cloudy, sunny, etc.)
description: Weather description (e.g. light rain, heavy snow, etc.)
icon: Weather icon code
stations: Weather station code
pressure: Air pressure (in millibars)
